---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="How Much Does a Website Cost in Hampshire? [2025 Guide]" 
  description="Transparent guide to website costs in Hampshire. From £500 to £10,000+, understand what you get at each price point. Free consultation available."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-50/30 to-primary-100/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
        Hampshire Business Guide 2025
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        How Much Does a <span class="text-primary-500">Website Cost</span> in Hampshire?
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A transparent breakdown of what Hampshire businesses actually pay for professional web design. 
        No hidden costs, no surprises—just honest pricing.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
          Get Your Free Quote
        </a>
        <a href="#pricing-table" class="border-2 border-primary-500 text-primary-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
          See Pricing Table
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you're a Hampshire business owner researching website costs, you've probably seen prices ranging from 
        £500 to £50,000. That's not particularly helpful when you're trying to budget.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        As a Hampshire-based web design agency with 15+ years of experience, we've built hundreds of websites 
        for local businesses. In this guide, we'll break down exactly what you can expect to pay—and what you 
        actually get at different price points.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-primary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg my-8">
        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">
          <strong>Quick Answer:</strong> Most Hampshire small businesses pay between £1,500 and £5,000 for a 
          professional brochure website. E-commerce sites typically range from £3,000 to £10,000+ depending on complexity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Affects Website Cost -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        What Factors Affect Website Cost?
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Number of Pages</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            A simple 5-page site (Home, About, Services, Contact) costs less than a 20+ page site with complex navigation.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">E-commerce Functionality</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Online stores require product pages, payment processing, stock management—adding significant complexity.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.433-4.832A2 2 0 0115 9.341V7a2 2 0 00-2-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2v1a2 2 0 01-2 2.174A2 2 0 019 10.684V12a2 2 0 002 2h2.17a2 2 0 001.66-.86l.42-.6a2 2 0 013.24 0l.42.6a2 2 0 001.66.86H17a2 2 0 002-2v-1.316a2 2 0 01-.567-1.474V7a2 2 0 00-2-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2v1a2 2 0 00-2 2v2.174a2 2 0 01-.433 1.258l-.434.516a2 2 0 00.433 2.642l3 2.4a2 2 0 002.502 0l3-2.4a2 2 0 00.433-2.642l-.434-.516z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Custom Design vs Template</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Bespoke designs tailored to your brand cost more than modified templates—but convert better.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Content Management System</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            WordPress sites cost differently than custom-built headless sites or page builder platforms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Table -->
  <section id="pricing-table" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">
        Website Pricing for Hampshire Businesses
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Typical costs you can expect from Hampshire web design agencies in 2025
      </p>
      
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-primary-500 text-white">
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">Website Type</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold">Typical Cost</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">What You Get</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">Best For</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">DIY / Template</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£10-50/mo</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Wix/Squarespace template, basic pages, limited customization</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Micro businesses with no budget</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Brochure Website<br><span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">(5-10 pages)</span></td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£1,500-3,500</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Custom design, mobile-responsive, CMS, basic SEO, contact forms</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Most small businesses, trades, professionals</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Brochure Website<br><span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">(10-20 pages)</span></td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£3,500-7,000</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Advanced design, portfolio/gallery, blog, enhanced SEO, animations</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Growing businesses, tourism, professional services</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">E-commerce<br><span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">(Small shop)</span></td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£3,000-6,000</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">WooCommerce setup, 20-50 products, payment gateway, basic shipping</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Local retailers, craft businesses</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">E-commerce<br><span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">(Medium shop)</span></td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£6,000-15,000</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Advanced WooCommerce, 100+ products, custom features, integrations</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Established retailers, multi-category stores</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Bespoke / Complex</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£7,000-20,000+</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Custom functionality, headless CMS, integrations, membership systems</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Large businesses, unique requirements</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
        * Prices are estimates based on Hampshire market rates. Actual costs depend on specific requirements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Our Hampshire Web Design Pricing
      </h2>
      
      <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-primary-200">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          At Meon Valley Web, we believe in transparent pricing. Most of our Hampshire clients 
          fall into these brackets:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-4 border-b border-primary-200">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Starter Website</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Up to 5 pages, template-based</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£1,200-2,000</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-4 border-b border-primary-200">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Business Website</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">5-10 pages, custom design, CMS</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£2,500-4,500</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-4 border-b border-primary-200">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">E-commerce Starter</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Up to 50 products, WooCommerce</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£3,500-6,000</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Bespoke Project</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Custom functionality, large sites</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">£6,000+</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
          All projects include mobile-responsive design, basic SEO, CMS training, and 30 days of support. 
          Hosting and maintenance available from £50/month.
        </p>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
            Get Your Free, No-Obligation Quote
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to invest in your Hampshire business?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8">
        Get a transparent, no-obligation quote for your web design project.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-primary-500 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
          Request Your Free Quote
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
          View Our Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
